title: LA Reid Pt. 3
itunes:title: LA Reid Pt. 3
description:
The third and final part of LA Reid's epic QLS interview covers the founding of LaFace Records and some rarely discussed history surrounding OutKast and TLC. LA also looks at his time leading Def Jam and identifying Rihanna and Kanye West as the label's new stars.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
